gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 133, Grizzlies 109
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the Grizzlies, 133-109. Jordan Clarkson recorded 20 points, six rebounds, and five assists for the Jazz, with Lauri Markkanen adding 19 points (4-6 3PM) and 11 rebounds in the victory. Desmond Bane tallied 21 points and three rebounds for the Grizzlies in the losing effort. The Jazz improve to 2-3 on the season, while the Grizzlies fall to 0-5.
